za 'Kralja lavova' za Toma.

154
00:09:58,185 --> 00:09:59,485
U redu mali...

155
00:09:59,564 --> 00:10:01,954
lagano primi za kraj...

156
00:10:02,022 --> 00:10:04,392
i udari, hajde.

157
00:10:06,378 --> 00:10:09,838
Krasno, sad će mi uprljati štap pijeskom
samo da Poncho ne uprlja cipele.

158
00:10:09,946 --> 00:10:13,436
